&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzQwNzI3OA==&amp;amp;mid=2651381518&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=30a7d59fef214a79b46609a0e3236891&amp;amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;失败的逻辑读书笔记-失败的根源是目标不清晰&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;








